                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Değerlerimiz</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold">Dürüstlük ve Şeffaflık</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Müvekkillerimizle açık ve dürüst iletişim kurarak güven inşa ediyoruz.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
